comments: Murray (ATL) jumps vertically and marginal contact occurs with Sochan (SAS) as the briefly come together during the transition play.
Play is blown dead to correct a clock malfunction as the clock continues to run after the made basket, and before the inbounds pass.
Collins (SAS) legally contests Murray's (ATL) jump shot attempt.
After Collins (SAS) bobbles the ball upon receiving the pass, Capela (ATL) legally contests Collins' layup attempt.
Capela (ATL) firms up on his right foot in Sochan's (SAS) path and absorbs the marginal contact as they come together during the pick.
Sochan (SAS) releases the inbound pass within 5 seconds.
Capela (ATL) makes clean contact with the ball to block Wembanyama's (SAS) layup attempt prior to any incidental follow-through arm contact occurring.
Sochan (SAS) adjusts to Young's (ATL) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together on the perimeter at the start of Young's drive.
Sochan (SAS) moves into and initiates contact with Young's (ATL) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (ATL) initiates contact with Collins (SAS), which affects his ability to make his intended pass.
Johnson (SAS) quickly slides his hand off of Young's (ATL) side and marginal contact occurs during the screen.
Okongwu (ATL) establishes himself in Johnson's (SAS) path and slightly extends his arms out as marginal contact occurs when they briefly engage during the screen.
Johnson (SAS) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Young (ATL) legally contests Sochan's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Sochan (SAS) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Okongwu (ATL) legally contests Wembanyama's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Johnson (SAS) and Murray (ATL) both make clean contact with the ball during their pursuit for the rebound.
Sochan (SAS) makes clean contact with the ball and deflects the inbound pass away from Okongwu (ATL).

Young (ATL) beats Sochan (SAS) to the spot and firms up on his left foot to establish himself in a legal guarding position in his path.  Sochan then drives through Young's space and dislodges him from his defensive position during the driving shot attempt.
